Project: Riverworld — the muster roll
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)
License: MIT

Philip José Farmer's Riverworld saga (5 novels, 1971–1983) sorted by role on the
River: the Seekers (Burton, Alice, Frigate, Nur), the Builders (Twain, Richthofen,
Firebrass), the Tyrants (King John, the River Kingdoms), the Second Chance (La Viro,
Göring), the Companions (Kazz, Monat, Cyrano, Tom Mix, Gilgamesh), the Ethicals
(the Council of Twelve, the Agents), and — set apart — the Renegade (X / the
Mysterious Stranger / Loga). Every member carries a .agent (who/do/belong) in
agents/, generated from roster.json by gen_agents.py. Characters by Philip José
Farmer and history, inspiration only.
